{
  "id": "69d57360a0547aaf28b3c690",
  "title": "Macでウィンドウ閉じてもアプリは残ってるけど閉じる？",
  "created": 1775596387,
  "updated": 1775660259,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d57360a0547aaf28b3c690",
      "text": "Macでウィンドウ閉じてもアプリは残ってるけど閉じる？",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775596387,
      "updated": 1775596387
    },
    {
      "id": "69d573610000000000f04eaf",
      "text": "\t割と閉じる[sta.icon][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775596387,
      "updated": 1775659255
    },
    {
      "id": "69d573610000000000f04eb0",
      "text": "\tあんまり閉じない[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775596387,
      "updated": 1775659920
    },
    {
      "id": "69d573650000000000f04eb1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775596391,
      "updated": 1775596391
    },
    {
      "id": "69d573650000000000f04eb2",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775596391,
      "updated": 1775596393
    },
    {
      "id": "69d573670000000000f04eb4",
      "text": "\t片付ける側の人間だからか、[altab]の選択肢は一つでも減らしたいのでいったん閉じちゃう",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775596393,
      "updated": 1775659225
    },
    {
      "id": "69d573660000000000f04eb3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775596393,
      "updated": 1775596393
    },
    {
      "id": "69d668f8000000000054ce60",
      "text": "[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775659257,
      "updated": 1775659260
    },
    {
      "id": "69d668fb000000000054ce62",
      "text": " 最近Macを使い始めたので気になっている",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775659260,
      "updated": 1775659274
    },
    {
      "id": "69d66a280000000000af9e51",
      "text": " [Dockのアイコンの下に点が残る]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775659561,
      "updated": 1775659902
    },
    {
      "id": "69d66972000000000056cc36",
      "text": " あれ？でもどういう時に残るのかよくわかってないかも",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775659379,
      "updated": 1775659391
    },
    {
      "id": "69d6697f000000000056cc37",
      "text": "  残らないこともある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775659392,
      "updated": 1775659396
    },
    {
      "id": "69d6690b000000000054ce63",
      "text": " 　おおまかには通知・同期・再生など継続的な処理があるものは残る[Claude.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775659275,
      "updated": 1775659888
    },
    {
      "id": "69d66b2c0000000000af9e53",
      "text": " 　アプリ側の実装で決まる[Claude.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775659820,
      "updated": 1775659888
    },
    {
      "id": "69d668fb000000000054ce61",
      "text": " 　 NSApplication の [applicationShouldTerminateAfterLastWindowClosed] というメソッドが true を返すとウィンドウを閉じた時に終了し、false なら残る",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775659260,
      "updated": 1775659888
    },
    {
      "id": "69d66b0d0000000000af9e52",
      "text": " [Cmd+Q]で閉じるらしい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775659789,
      "updated": 1775660259
    },
    {
      "id": "69d66cd50000000000af9e54",
